# Multi-file compile sample (merged by moonsightc into game.msb).
# Host demo.yuki only ships the entry file; garden also lives in main.yuki
# so browser play works. This file keeps a distinct side scene for merge tests.

- scene "side_room"
@meta.id "side_room.op1"
y:Side room — present only in the multi-file project graph.
@var.set "saw_side" true
@flow.yield
